# Native folders 전체 — EAS 가 매 빌드 fresh prebuild 강제.
# 이전엔 prebuild 가 "ios directory already exists" 로 스킵되어 react-native-google-mobile-ads
# plugin 의 GADApplicationIdentifier inject 누락 → TestFlight #55, #56 SIGABRT.
# .gitignore 는 .easignore 에 영향 없음 (EAS 는 untracked 도 업로드).
/android
/ios
android
ios
/lib
/macos
/windows
/linux
/test
/build
/dist
/web-build

# Design & docs
*.pen
/screenshots
/export
*.tar.gz

# Dev tools
.claude
.git
.vscode
*.md
!README.md

# Node / Expo caches (EAS reinstalls dependencies)
**/node_modules
.expo
.expo-shared
.metro-cache

# Large artifacts
/fortune-transfer-bundle-*
/pencil*

# Env & secrets (EAS pulls from its own secrets)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.p8
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
